data.description: **$10,000 Buyer Closing Cost Assistance!**Stylish 4 Bedroom Home in Frenship ISD.  Discover this refined residence in Quincy Park, prized for its exceptional schools, playa lake, playground, and close proximity to shopping and restaurants. The open layout and spacious living area creates an inviting atmosphere, perfect for gatherings. The living room boasts waterproof cushion-back vinyl plank flooring, combining style with practicality. The kitchen features exquisite floor tile and granite countertops.  The master suite offers a private retreat with a separate tub, shower, and double closets. A versatile fourth bedroom provides options for an office or craft room. The backyard is a spacious with an extended patio and storage shed, ideal for outdoor living. This home offers a blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Experience modern living in this cherished community.
